Name: Escape Dark Tunnels
About the game: Escape Dark Tunnels is a puzzle game where the player gets trapped underground being chased by mysterious creatures. You will have to use your ingenuity and logic to escape from the tunnels. A first person experience where the player will have to face difficult puzzles, mazes and jumps in a dark and mysterious environment. Get out of Escape Dark Tunnels alive!
